headline: Major game studio Ubisoft stuns investors with last-minute earnings delay, share halt
summary: The video game industry has been running low on HP all 2025, fighting boss battles against studio layoffs, game delays, and financial troubles. Now, it appears that releasing earnings in a timely manner is also proving difficult, at least for the French game studio behind franchises such as ...
